        "release_notes": {
            "en-US": "v3. Hardly tested. Should at least not be completely broken.\n\nReport issues on the gitlab tracker, thx!\n\n<a href=\"https://prod.outgoing.prod.webservices.mozgcp.net/v1/7bb962b9477a9936a2c6f9f14c4d265fd387b79bdc223370753773b53dc779dc/https%3A//gitlab.com/losnappas/live-recorder/-/issues\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://gitlab.com/losnappas/live-recorder/-/issues</a>"
